  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study of time usage of anesthesia team inside the main operating room compares between 2
      groups of

        -  Performing regional anesthesia inside the operating room

        -  Performing regional anesthesia in the block room

      Study purpose: How much will the investigators save time in the main operating room if we
      perform the regional anesthesia in the block room?
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Anesthesia-controlled time means anesthesia pre-procedure time plus anesthesia post-procedure
      time.

      We also compares the anesthesia-controlled time in 3 groups of

        -  general anesthesia

        -  regional anesthesia

        -  general anesthesia combined with regional anesthesia
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
